description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 4, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 20, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 3 for East, 5 for South, and Stringalong for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80045-73574-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [20 Votes, Common]
